		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Since I program more in HLL languages like C++, I'd say my time works out more like this:
<br />
<br />Designing / Concept:  85%
<br />Programming:  15%
<br />Optimizing:  0% (let the compiler do it)

		

		</td>
