		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />For me it depends a lot on the project and the platform.
<br />
<br />In high level languages it's usually like this:
<br />
<br />Designing: 20%
<br />Optimizing the design: 10%
<br />Programming: 60%
<br />Optimizing the code: 10%
<br />
<br />But in assembly it's more like this:
<br />
<br />Designing: 30%
<br />Optimizing the design: 30%
<br />Programming: 38%
<br />Optimizing the code: 2%

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


